metadata.name: Doodle Pet #1
metadata.description: Doodle Sanctuary Pets is a series of meticulously curated 3-Dimensional Animals for the Metaverse. An unreal engine-powered Doodle Pet will be available for use in the Doodle Estate ecosystem and will be fully interactive. The Pet Pass will grant you access to a 3-dimensional (3D) metadata refresh in May 2022. These Pets can further be staked at one of the first wildlife sanctuaries (Doodle Animal Sanctuary) created in the Metaverse.
